Monster Python + Python Kingdom (The Python) | 2 Full Killer Snake Movies | Mythology Movies

Monster Python: A film crew shooting in an abandoned village use a collection of large eggs that they find, as props for their movie. Only to discover that the mother of the eggs would kill to get them back.
Stars: Wu Hao, Du Wu Lin, Wang Xin Man

Python Kingdom (The Python): A secluded mountain village in northern Fujian is in a state of panic after a wedding party was invaded by the Python King and his giant snake. After the groom slays the beast and throws it on the alter, the python king vows to get his revenge, leaving the village in fear for their lives.
Stars: Naomen Eerdeni, Eric Suen
